{"tid":971662,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個另一半做過令你感動既事","createTime":"2019-01-06T20:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T12:50:20.000Z","uid":136933,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"abf3e8f2ceafc6209fb71d01489ba7e6497b3ac9","tid":971662,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T20:46:56.000Z","msg":"中學時候拍拖 但另一半已經做緊野<br />\n成日見到啲同學返學放學可以一齊 <br />\n考試可以一齊溫書 互相教大家<br />\n都咪話唔羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一晚同佢傾電話既時候<br />\n無意中講起：好羨慕啲同學放學有得著住校服拍拖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知第二日佢話接我放學<br />\n我一出校門<br />\n見到佢著住套中學校服等我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個下係呆撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢同我講 我就陪唔到你返學架喇 但係今日就當住我地係隔離學校既情侶 放學拍住拖先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成件事好戇鳩<br />\n但個下真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我隨口講既野佢真係走左去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0a4f633c83ea4bf3d0be12db9d0e9981968035","tid":971662,"uid":140357,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"abf3e8f2ceafc6209fb71d01489ba7e6497b3ac9","tid":971662,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T20:46:56.000Z","msg":"中學時候拍拖 但另一半已經做緊野<br />\n成日見到啲同學返學放學可以一齊 <br />\n考試可以一齊溫書 互相教大家<br />\n都咪話唔羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一晚同佢傾電話既時候<br />\n無意中講起：好羨慕啲同學放學有得著住校服拍拖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知第二日佢話接我放學<br />\n我一出校門<br />\n見到佢著住套中學校服等我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個下係呆撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢同我講 我就陪唔到你返學架喇 但係今日就當住我地係隔離學校既情侶 放學拍住拖先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成件事好戇鳩<br />\n但個下真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我隨口講既野佢真係走左去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T20:51:42.000Z","msg":"好男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想做e d sweet野"},{"pid":"b2fb8b0c033ecb5690f05f70b7d695712cb03328","tid":971662,"uid":201604,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T20:52:20.000Z","msg":"冇另一半"},{"pid":"014a3e873f374ad1fe8a6fcaee2acfa440c65d4e","tid":971662,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T21:01:10.000Z","msg":"外國讀書果時,同另一半無住HALL,係學校附近租屋住<br />\n有一次我病得好重<br />\n佢唔單止照顧我起居飲食,<br />\n仲幫我手洗對襪,無錯,臭襪<br />\n一邊洗佢一邊話咁大個女都未試過<br />\n果一刻好感動"},{"pid":"a27e2ee7ee0b30872298557d7a9f1670a7afbe07","tid":971662,"uid":228266,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T21:13:38.000Z","msg":"有次抄電單車，手腳面都係傷口，唔係好郁到。<br />\n所有日常野都要佢幫我，佢都無任何怨言。<br />\n沖涼，文屎，洗傷口，食飯... 全部都幫我。"},{"pid":"a787c3f6e4d3ee6e765ccca43fe81407f8c6a0e5","tid":971662,"uid":15516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"送左個日曆比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3cd8a77f76de0979c13a3f4097e84c02d54d24","tid":971662,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a787c3f6e4d3ee6e765ccca43fe81407f8c6a0e5","tid":971662